  395                 | ALTER . TABLE NAME CHANGE COLUMN NAME NAME data_type column_atts opt_col_position
  396                 | ALTER . TABLE NAME CHANGE NAME NAME data_type column_atts opt_col_position
  837 stmt: ALTER . TRIGGER NAME ENABLE
  838     | ALTER . TRIGGER NAME DISABLE
